&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;We are looking for an Account Executive in Civilian - Tribes to join our Sales and Go-to-Market team. &lt;strong&gt;This role is based in the D.C. area&lt;/strong&gt;, reporting to the Regional Director. You will be part of a global group of professionals passionate about delighting our customers, nurturing trusted partnerships, and sharing expertise to drive a secure, cloud-enabled digital future. By demonstrating the power and agility of cloud transformation, you will help cement our position as the world leader in cloud security.&lt;/p&gt;
