&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an Account Executive to join our team. This is a Hybrid, Mumbai role, reporting to the Regional Sales Director in the Commercial Sales department. You will join a global group of professionals passionate about delighting customers and driving a secure, cloud-enabled digital future as the world leader in cloud security. As a key member of the Sales and Go-to-Market team, you will demonstrate the power and agility of cloud transformation while nurturing trusted partnerships to achieve shared success.&lt;/p&gt;
