&lt;li&gt;Act as the GM of your business by creating strategic success plans that include coverage, target prospects, and marketing campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement world-class sales methodologies to consistently overachieve on quarterly and annual revenue goals&lt;/li&gt;
